21:59.819 --> 22:01.320
Aw, stop it.
Yeah.
(laughter)

22:02.455 --> 22:03.556
Come on. Give me a hoot.

22:03.590 --> 22:04.824
Hoot!

22:04.857 --> 22:05.725
Hoot!
